      "description": "Looking for a reliable ride that gets the job done? This car is in fair condition and ready for its next owner! It shows some honest wear and tear from its years on the road, but it still runs strong and offers a dependable driving experience for anyone looking for great value. It\u2019s a solid, practical choice that\u2019s priced to sell!",
