    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior paint still holds a nice luster, though you will find some minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper from normal use. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of odors, with only light wear visible on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car is sound, with all features functioning as intended and a consistent service history. It\u2019s a reliable, honest car that is ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
