    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my awesome ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in great shape for its next adventure! It drives like a dream and has been super well-maintained. If you\u2019re looking for a solid, dependable car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, this is definitely the one for you. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power delivery through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The chassis remains composed thanks to a factory-spec limited-slip differential and recent rear subframe reinforcement. Maintenance is up to date, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and valve clearance adjustment. While showing minor aesthetic wear consistent with its mileage, the mechanical integrity is robust, offering the tactile steering response and high-RPM crescendo that defines the M-division's golden era.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Clean title. Regularly serviced. Minor cosmetic wear. Runs well. Reliable transport.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents the ideal find for a driver seeking both reliability and a polished presence. The exterior retains a beautiful shine, showing only the slight, inevitable signs of careful road use like minor stone chips on the hood. Inside, the cabin has been kept in impressive order; the seats are firm and free of significant wear, and the non-smoker interior ensures a fresh environment. Every electronic feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the infotainment system, operates flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts with precision, backed by a comprehensive service record that proves this car was never neglected. It is a solid, dependable, and attractive choice for anyone looking for a premium driving experience without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
